Sentencas: An artificial neural network (ANN) and a genetic algorithm (GA) are employed to model and optimize cell parameters to improve the performance of singular, intermediate-temperature, solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Modeling and Optimization of Anode-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Cell Parameters via Artificial Neural Network and Genetic Algorithm

Sentencas: The ANN model uses a feed-forward neural network with an error back-propagation algorithm.
Titulo: Modeling and Optimization of Anode-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Cell Parameters via Artificial Neural Network and Genetic Algorithm

Sentencas: The ANN is trained using experimental data as a black-box without using physical models.
Titulo: Modeling and Optimization of Anode-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Cell Parameters via Artificial Neural Network and Genetic Algorithm

Sentencas: The developed model is able to predict the performance of the SOFC.
Titulo: Modeling and Optimization of Anode-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Cell Parameters via Artificial Neural Network and Genetic Algorithm

Sentencas: An optimization algorithm is utilized to select the optimal SOFC parameters.
Titulo: Modeling and Optimization of Anode-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Cell Parameters via Artificial Neural Network and Genetic Algorithm

Sentencas: The optimal values of four cell parameters (anode support thickness, anode support porosity, electrolyte thickness, and functional layer cathode thickness) are determined by using the GA under different conditions.
Titulo: Modeling and Optimization of Anode-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Cell Parameters via Artificial Neural Network and Genetic Algorithm

Sentencas: The results show that these optimum cell parameters deliver the highest maximum power density under different constraints on the anode support thickness, porosity, and electrolyte thickness.
Titulo: Modeling and Optimization of Anode-Supported Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Cell Parameters via Artificial Neural Network and Genetic Algorithm
